      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Nov 2007 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/interface/hulu-registration/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Simple registration form. No captcha in this form, although that could change when they get out of private beta. Having to click the check button seems unnecessary. A javascript check on blur would be better. This form might benefit from a little chunking, e.g. simple hairlines between some fields. &lt;/p&gt;
